thread.title: Cris Hockey

author: Cris Hockey
title: Cris Hockey
text: Thank you to all at Property Now for the guidance & support provided in listing & selling my own home. And to anyone that wishes to do the same, please; read Andrew's book, follow it step by step, get a valuation done so that you are confident on what your home is worth and finally, presentation is KING! Invest in good photography. Keep up the great work Andrew.
